Loops:
    Loops help us repeat code till its false

    Syntax:
    while(condition){
    //code that we want to repeat
    }

    "++" = increment operator (increase number by 1)
    "--" = decrement operator (decrease number by 1)
    % = means multiples of a number

    Do While Loops:
    Prints/execute code once THEN checks the condtion.

    While Loops:
    Checks condtion first THEN prints code.